@TheIdealCard comes as a card, ring, key holder, wallet, smartphone sticky, and many more items for added convenience.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

The @waldanwatches Pastel Edition Capsule Collection is now available for sale! Featuring three meticulously designed new models; Sky Blue (ref. 0196BL), Blush Pink (ref. 0196P) and Canary Yellow (ref. 0196C), these limited edition watches are limited to 300 pcs. 

Crafted with the signature details that make a watch a Waldan, these models offer a more vibrant color way into the Heritage collection. All watches are individually hand assembled in the United States, certified and tested under a proprietary zero defect protocol and are powered by the jeweled and all-metal, American Made “Ameriquartz” cal. 70200 movement that is fully serviceable and warrantied for 5 years. 

Available for sale now at waldanwatches.com, free shipping available for domestic orders.
